reviews.review_text: St. Stephen a little plodding It is amazing how different the St. Stephen's back east where from this one. While I love the Dead this one sounds like its on Tylenol PM compared to MSG & Hartford. I was at Hartford (the MSG show was the first MSG show I missed in the 80's!!doooh!) and it was so much more full of energy. I guess that's why most of the breakouts and cool stuff happened on tour and not in Cali (at least during the 80's and 90's).
